title: "functional and sculptural ceramics and art for everyone",
announcement: "Welcome to Light a Fire on Etsy. Here art meets life through affordable and high-end handmade objects made for everyone. I am the owner/operator Frederick Doerpholz a ceramic and multimedia artist in Denver, Colorado. Light a Fire offers a unique assortment of my work, including dinnerware, mugs, cups, bowls, wall mounted and free standing sculptures, and other functional and nonfunctional ceramic items. Please enjoy and Thank You for your visit!",
currency_code: "USD",
is_vacation: false,
vacation_message: "Dear Friends; I will have the shop closed for a few days but we&#39;ll be back open bright and Early on Tuesday the 11th of August 2015. If you need anything please don’t hesitate to contact me as I will still be answering messages/emails. Thanks, Frederick",
sale_message: "Thank you for choosing to Light a Fire in your life. I hope you enjoy your purchase and that this item continues to inspire you always. If you have comments or questions after you receive your item, or have an issue with the purchase, feel free to contact me personally at fdoerpholz@hotmail.com and thank you again for your support. If something arrives broken please document via photographs and include in your correspondence to help with replacement. Keep in mind, handmade objects are hard if almost impossible to recreate exactly, but I will do my best to make sure you are satisfied. Sincerely, Frederick Doerpholz",
digital_sale_message: null,
