title: "Handmade & Monogrammed Gifts in Leather, Stone, Metal",
announcement: "At Killorglin Creations, we manufacture unique monogrammed, custom gifts in stone, leather, wood, glass and metal. We have gifts for individuals as well as wedding party gifts and favors - all handcrafted in our shop in Methuen, Massachusetts. All items are custom made, so our average processing time is 12-15 days plus transit. Please follow us on Twitter: @KCGiftware for COUPON CODES and new product updates! ",
currency_code: "USD",
is_vacation: false,
vacation_message: "We are now in &quot;vacation mode&quot; and not accepting any new orders. Since each item is a custom order, we need the time to make them. Due to the amount of in house orders and the closeness of Christmas, we will not be accepting any new orders for Christmas deliveries. We will reopen the store Wed Dec 17th, but any order placed then will not arrive by Christmas. All orders that have already been placed are being worked on and will ship by Dec 18th, so if you have an order with us already, no need to check on it, we have it and it will be shipped by the 18th. We always send the tracking number when an order ships. You can still contact us through this Etsy email. DO NOT USE REGULAR EMAIL - ONLY THIS ETSY EMAIL SYSTEM. Please understand that we are hard at work on your custom order, so please only contact us with important questions, as answering emails takes away from our production time. Reference your ORDER DATE and the name of the person it is being SHIPPED TO. ",
sale_message: "We thank you for your order, and hope that you enjoy your purchase. Follow us on TWITTER for Coupon Codes and product updates: @KCgiftware Thank you, The Ness&#39; Killorglin Creations",
